            <h3 id="newyear123119" style="text-align: center; letter-spacing: 5px; background-color: #EC257C; color: white;">THE ARGENTINE ARTIST</h3>

            <blockquote class="blockquote text-center" style="margin-bottom: 16px; margin-top: 16px;">
                <p class="mb-0" style="color: black!important;">"You must be willing to leave the life you planned in order to find the one waiting for you."</p>
                <footer class="blockquote-footer"><cite title="Source Title">Joseph Campbell</cite></footer>
            </blockquote>

            <p style="color: black!important;">
                Jorge Adeler is one of those rare artisans that perfectly combines raw beauty with high end polish. He seeks out and highlights the natural elements of a gemstone with a creative and intelligent design concept, resulting in perfect luxurious harmony.
            </p>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md">
