            <p style="color: black!important;">
                Mindfulness is a facet of life that we can never truly have enough of. A new year begins and to me that means new and perhaps pre-existing things to be mindful of and for. 
                Whether it's your loved ones, your home or even your favorite bauble that you are in a state of gratitude for, I say good for you!
            </p>

